name: I Don't Need Their Scum, Either (V)
Lore: 'Of all the scum and villainy Lando had dealt with (pirates, smugglers, con-artists, thieves, swindlers, politicians and Imperial lackeys), he hated bounty hunters the most.',
Text: 'USED: Cancel Lando System? OR If Lando piloting Falcon, it draws two battle destiny if not able to otherwise.LOST: Retrieve your just lost gambler (except Dash) into hand. OR Place a copy of Eject! Eject! deployed on table in your Used Pile.',
